---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Happy Hour">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Happy Hour</h1>

    <p>
      <strong>Happy Hour</strong> is a learning accountability project for programmers.
      The idea is simple: commit your daily learning notes to git, and the website
      tracks your streak automatically.
    </p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>

    <ol>
      <li><strong>Fork</strong> the repo and create your directory</li>
      <li>Run <code>sh init.sh yourname</code> to set up your workspace</li>
      <li>Each day, run <code>./newdaily topic</code> to create a new note</li>
      <li>Write your notes in the generated markdown file</li>
      <li>Run <code>./push</code> to commit and push</li>
      <li>Your check-in is recorded and your streak updates on the next deploy</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Philosophy</h2>

    <blockquote>
      Learn anything at anytime in one hour.
    </blockquote>

    <p>
      It doesn't matter what you learn. It matters that you learn consistently.
      One hour a day, every day. Write down what you learned, what confused you,
      and what questions you have. Over time, you'll build a personal knowledge base
      and a habit that compounds.
    </p>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Content</strong>: Markdown files in git</li>
      <li><strong>Site</strong>: Astro static site generator</li>
      <li><strong>Hosting</strong>: Cloudflare Pages</li>
      <li><strong>Deployment</strong>: Automatic on push to master</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Join</h2>

    <p>
      Want to join? Open an issue or submit a PR on
      <a href="https://github.com/bricktile/happy-hour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about ol, .about ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
